# Code Quality & Security Patterns - FDK Warning Fixes

**Load this file when:**
- `fdk validate` shows function complexity > 5
- User asks to fix lint warnings or code quality issues
- Async scoping / race condition warnings appear
- "Expected rejection to be handled" warnings
- Deprecated API usage warnings (Freshservice v1)
- Empty block statement warnings
- iparam secure warnings
- **Security audit or vulnerability check needed**
- **Hardcoded credentials detected**
- **Injection vulnerabilities suspected**
- **Sensitive data logging (args.iparams) detected**
- **XSS patterns (innerHTML with variables) found**

