## Pattern 4: Deprecated API Migration (Freshservice v1 → v2)

**Warning:** `possible deprecated API usage detected`

### Endpoint Migration Table

| Deprecated (v1) | Current (v2) |
|-----------------|--------------|
| `/helpdesk/tickets.json` | `/api/v2/tickets` |
| `/helpdesk/tickets/{id}.json` | `/api/v2/tickets/{id}` |
| `/itil/tickets.json` | `/api/v2/tickets` |
| `/itil/assets.json` | `/api/v2/assets` |
| `/itil/requesters.json` | `/api/v2/requesters` |
| `/itil/agents.json` | `/api/v2/agents` |
| `/itil/changes.json` | `/api/v2/changes` |
| `/itil/problems.json` | `/api/v2/problems` |
| `/itil/releases.json` | `/api/v2/releases` |

### Update config/requests.json

```json
// ❌ WRONG: v1 API
{
  "getTicket": {
    "schema": {
      "method": "GET",
      "host": "<%= iparam.domain %>.freshservice.com",
      "path": "/helpdesk/tickets/<%= context.id %>.json",
      "headers": {
        "Authorization": "Basic <%= context.auth %>"
      }
    }
  }
}

// ✅ CORRECT: v2 API
{
  "getTicket": {
    "schema": {
      "method": "GET",
      "host": "<%= iparam.domain %>.freshservice.com",
      "path": "/api/v2/tickets/<%= context.id %>",
      "headers": {
        "Authorization": "Basic <%= context.auth %>",
        "Content-Type": "application/json"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

### Update Response Parsing

```javascript
// v1 API response structure
// { helpdesk_ticket: { id: 1, subject: "..." } }

// v2 API response structure
// { ticket: { id: 1, subject: "..." } }

// ❌ WRONG: v1 parsing
const ticket = JSON.parse(response.response).helpdesk_ticket;

// ✅ CORRECT: v2 parsing
const ticket = JSON.parse(response.response).ticket;
```

