## Pattern 8: Unused Parameters

**Warning:** `'args' is defined but never used.`

```javascript
// ❌ WRONG: Unused parameter
exports = {
  onAppInstallHandler: function(args) {
    console.log('App installed');
  }
};

// ✅ CORRECT: Remove parameter (FDK allows optional args)
exports = {
  onAppInstallHandler: function() {
    console.log('App installed');
  }
};

// ✅ CORRECT: Use the parameter
exports = {
  onAppInstallHandler: function(args) {
    console.log('App installed with iparams:', Object.keys(args.iparams));
  }
};
```

