## Quick Reference: Complexity Reduction Checklist

Before finalizing any function:

- [ ] Complexity ≤ 5? (Check with linter)
- [ ] No nested if/else more than 2 levels deep?
- [ ] Using lookup objects instead of if/else chains?
- [ ] Using guard clauses at function start?
- [ ] Using filter/map/reduce instead of loops with conditions?
- [ ] Single responsibility (one function = one task)?
- [ ] Helper functions for distinct operations?

## Quick Reference: Error Handling Checklist

- [ ] All `client.request.invoke()` calls have try/catch?
- [ ] All `$request.invokeTemplate()` calls have try/catch?
- [ ] All `.then()` chains have `.catch()`?
- [ ] Event listeners wrap async calls in try/catch?
- [ ] SMI functions return `{ success: true/false }` pattern?
- [ ] Fatal errors show user-friendly message?

## Quick Reference: Async Scoping Checklist

- [ ] Using IIFE pattern `(async function() { ... })()`?
- [ ] No `let` variables assigned in async callbacks?
- [ ] Dependencies passed as parameters, not globals?
- [ ] State object pattern for shared state?

