## 🔒 Pattern 9: Security Checks (MANDATORY)

**These patterns MUST be checked during code generation and validation. Violations are BLOCKING.**

### 9.1 Credential Exposure Detection

**NEVER hardcode credentials in code:**

```javascript
// ❌ CRITICAL: Hardcoded API key
const apiKey = 'sk-1234567890abcdef';

// ❌ CRITICAL: Hardcoded password
const password = 'mysecretpassword';

// ❌ CRITICAL: Hardcoded token
const token = 'Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...';

// ✅ CORRECT: Use iparams
const apiKey = args.iparams.api_key;
```

**Patterns to detect (regex):**
```javascript
/api[_-]?key\s*[:=]\s*['"][^'"]{10,}['"]/i  // Hardcoded API keys
/password\s*[:=]\s*['"][^'"]+['"]/i          // Hardcoded passwords
/secret\s*[:=]\s*['"][^'"]{5,}['"]/i         // Hardcoded secrets
/token\s*[:=]\s*['"][^'"]{20,}['"]/i         // Hardcoded tokens
/Bearer\s+[A-Za-z0-9\-_\.]{20,}/             // Hardcoded Bearer tokens
```

### 9.2 Command/Code Injection Prevention

**NEVER pass user input to dangerous operations:**

```javascript
// ❌ CRITICAL: Command injection vulnerability
exports = {
  executeCommand: async function(args) {
    await $request.invokeTemplate('runScript', { body: JSON.stringify(args) });
  }
};

// ❌ CRITICAL: Code execution
eval(args.code);
new Function(args.script)();

// ✅ CORRECT: Use allowlists
const ALLOWED_COMMANDS = ['status', 'health', 'list'];
exports = {
  executeCommand: async function(args) {
    if (!ALLOWED_COMMANDS.includes(args.command)) {
      return { success: false, error: 'Command not allowed' };
    }
    // Execute predefined operation
  }
};
```

**Patterns to detect:**
```javascript
/eval\s*\(/                    // eval() usage
/new\s+Function\s*\(/          // new Function() usage
/executeCommand|runScript|runPowerShell/  // Command execution
```

### 9.3 Sensitive Data Logging Prevention

**NEVER log sensitive data:**

```javascript
// ❌ HIGH: Logs API keys and secrets
console.log('App installed', args.iparams);

// ❌ HIGH: Logs full args with potential secrets
console.log('Handler called', args);

// ❌ HIGH: Logs tokens
console.log('Auth token:', authToken);

// ✅ CORRECT: Log only confirmation
console.log('App installed successfully');

// ✅ CORRECT: Log only non-sensitive identifiers
console.log('Processing ticket:', args.data?.ticket?.id);
```

**Patterns to detect:**
```javascript
/console\.(log|info|debug)\s*\([^)]*iparams/i   // Logging iparams
/console\.(log|info|debug)\s*\([^)]*password/i  // Logging passwords
/console\.(log|info|debug)\s*\([^)]*token/i     // Logging tokens
/console\.(log|info|debug)\s*\([^)]*secret/i    // Logging secrets
/console\.(log|info|debug)\s*\([^)]*key/i       // Logging keys
```

### 9.4 XSS Prevention (innerHTML)

**NEVER insert unsanitized data into DOM:**

```javascript
// ❌ MEDIUM: XSS vulnerability
el.innerHTML = userData;
el.innerHTML = '<div>' + apiResponse + '</div>';
el.innerHTML = items.map(i => '<p>' + i.title + '</p>').join('');

// ✅ CORRECT: Use textContent for plain text
el.textContent = userData;

// ✅ CORRECT: Sanitize before innerHTML
function sanitize(str) {
  const div = document.createElement('div');
  div.textContent = str;
  return div.innerHTML;
}
el.innerHTML = '<div>' + sanitize(userData) + '</div>';

// ✅ CORRECT: Use Crayons components with static content
el.innerHTML = '<fw-inline-message type="success">Done</fw-inline-message>';
```

**Patterns to detect:**
```javascript
/innerHTML\s*=\s*[^'"`<]*[a-zA-Z_$][a-zA-Z0-9_$]*[^;]*;/  // innerHTML with variable
```

### 9.5 Sensitive Data Storage Prevention

**NEVER store secrets in visible locations:**

```javascript
// ❌ MEDIUM: Password in ticket notes
const note = 'Password: ' + generatedPassword;
await client.interface.trigger('addNote', { content: note });

// ❌ MEDIUM: Secret in localStorage
localStorage.setItem('apiKey', apiKey);

// ✅ CORRECT: Send via secure channel
await client.request.invoke('sendSecureEmail', {
  to: email,
  password: generatedPassword,
  expiresIn: '24h'
});
await client.interface.trigger('addNote', {
  content: 'Credentials sent to requester email. Expires in 24h.',
  isPrivate: true
});

// ✅ CORRECT: Store server-side
await $db.set('token', { value: encryptedToken });
```

